  "original_title": "33,600 \u0bb2\u0bc0\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bcb\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd  \u0baa\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0bb8\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Bowser accident with 33,600 liters of petrol",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "A bowser carrying petrol met with an accident at Halukama Hill on Meerikama Thangowita road today (23) afternoon.",
        "The bowser contained 33,600 liters of petrol which was transported from Muthurajawela to Peradana.",
        "Preliminary investigation has revealed that the accident took place due to a sudden backward movement of the bowser in the Halukama hill area."
      ],
